title: INEOS race ultralight Princeton CarbonWorks Peak 4550 carbon wheels at Tour de France
content:
Princeton CarbonWorks has four all-new ultralight, wavy Peak 4550 carbon wheelsets and one of them is being raced now by the Team INEOS Grenadiers at the Tour de France. Those Peak 4550 Launch Edition tubulars come in at a claimed 1071g for the 26mm wide rim brake wheels that the pros are racing now, but [â€¦]
